    <title>Stereo Enhancer</title>
    <p>
        PulseEffects uses the stereo enhancer plugin developed by
        <link href="https://calf-studio-gear.org">Calf Studio</link>. It uses Haas effect to improve the stereo signal.
    </p>
    <terms>
        <item>
            <title>
                <em style="strong">Balance</em>
            </title>
            <p>
                Set the balance between both channels
            </p>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>
                <em style="strong">Delay</em>
            </title>
            <p>
                Channel delay
            </p>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>
                <em style="strong">Mode</em>
            </title>
            <p>
                Choose how the middle signal is generated
            </p>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>
                <em style="strong">Side Gain</em>
            </title>
            <p>
                The level of the side signal
            </p>
        </item>
    </terms>
